These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
Transport: subway, bus
Food: grapes, mango
Hobby: board-games, gardening
Cigar: prince, game
Flower: bellflower, tulip
1. Hobby:gardening is on the right of Transport:subway##1
2. Cigar:game is on the far left##1
3. Food:grapes is in an even position##4
4. Flower:tulip is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Transport   | subway     | bus     |
| Food   | mango     | grapes |
| Hobby   | board-games | gardening  |
| Cigar           | game    | prince |
| Flower         | tulip   | bellflower       |

