.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
Flower: aconite, marigold
Hobby: dancing, chess
Birthday: august, march
Nationality: egyptian, mexican
Music-Genre: electronic, pop
1. Flower:aconite is on the right of Nationality:egyptian##1
2. Birthday:august == Hobby:dancing##1
3. Birthday:august is in an even position##4
4. Hobby:chess is on the left or right of Music-Genre:electronic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Flower      | marigold    | aconite |
| Hobby           | chess  | dancing     |
| Birthday   | march       | august      |
| Nationality           | egyptian        | mexican      |
| Music-Genre         | pop | electronic     |

